descriptionHtml:
This is my female nord. I created her a few hours ago after i reinstalled skyrim due to random crashing with a mod. I\'m still pissed off, Cause there was a patch for that mod that was making me crash and i didn\'t even realize until after i saw the patch for that mod. Sigh sigh. 

Her name is J. Just like my dark elf, Which she is based off of a little bit. She is put at the part in the keep after you have your bonds cut. Hadvar is waiting to continue in the hall way leading to the open area where you have your first fight. 

The mods i used are: 

Better Females By Bella W/Lesser Makeup: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2812

ApachiiSkyHair: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10168

MissAniThropes Mystic Eyes: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=12214

There are 3 Saves;

The first one is the original one.

The 2nd one is recreated to look exactly the same as the original except with siding with the stormcloak at the attack of helgen. 

The third one was a Face transfer using \"nycz\'s Skyrim Face Transfer program\" (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=15307), from the original to keep the same original look.

files.changelogHtml: I recreated my nord due to problems with my save. Hopefully no one else has the same problems i have. But i sided with the Stormcloak this time and she has red hair which you can always change later.
